      "content_html": "<p><img alt=\"Swimming demonstrated to be clinically effective in treating low back pain disability\" src=\"https://assets.newatlas.com/dims4/default/6bf1930/2147483647/strip/true/crop/6720x4480+0+0/resize/1440x960!/format/webp/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fnewatlas-brightspot.s3.ap-southeast-2.amazonaws.com%2F36%2Fb5%2F12e032834a4197388e9fe1d87b9a%2Fdepositphotos-180574616-xl.jpg\" /><p>In the first study of its kind, scientists have found that swimming can provide relief from chronic low back pain. The trial suggests this exercise is clinically effective for treating this hard-to-target condition.</p><p><a href=\"https://refractor.io/chronic-pain/back-pain-relief-swimming-trial/\">Continue Reading</a></p><p><b>Category:</b> <a href=\"https://refractor.io/chronic-pain\">Chronic Pain</a>, <a href=\"https://refractor.io/disease/\">Illnesses and conditions</a>, <a href=\"https://refractor.io/medical/\">Body and Mind</a>, <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/rf/\">Refractor: Science &amp; Health</a></p><p><b>Tags:</b> <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/tag/macquarie-university/\" rel=\"tag\">Macquarie University</a>, <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/tag/swimming/\" rel=\"tag\">Swimming</a>, <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/tag/physical-therapy/\" rel=\"tag\">Physical therapy</a>, <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/tag/physical-activity/\" rel=\"tag\">Physical activity</a>, <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/tag/exercise/\" rel=\"tag\">Exercise</a>, <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/tag/back-pain/\" rel=\"tag\">Back Pain</a>, <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/tag/pain/\" rel=\"tag\">Pain</a>, <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/tag/chronic-pain/\" rel=\"tag\">Chronic pain</a></p>",
